  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wanna be a part of this game?</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is my first game. If you have any suggestions or feedback, feel free to join the Discord and discuss with me.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My twitter: @ScarletAcademy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mail: <a href=\"mailto:multiturretacademy@gmail.com\">multiturretacademy@gmail.com</a></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our Discord! (link on the right) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/35b4a068f00f24e3b37d3ac0f70d25c6.avif?t=1774177854\" width=610 height=120 /></span></p></p><br><h1>Early access roadmap</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/63f7473aa183a0d40faae95bac414dab.avif?t=1774177854\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/2e41632d1c5fdfcbc0478de3114f6d82.avif?t=1774177854\" width=600 height=194 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome, comrade Commander!</h2><strong>Multi Turret Academy</strong> is a top-down tank action game with roguelike elements. Select your vehicle from a growing list of historical models, then equip dozens of weapons and upgrades to lead your local tank club to victory!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/9a2e480de691efde49f7d34bba905401.poster.avif?t=1774177854\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/9a2e480de691efde49f7d34bba905401.webm?t=1774177854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/9a2e480de691efde49f7d34bba905401.mp4?t=1774177854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Choice is Yours</h2>A growing selection of WWII tanks awaits, as you decide how to achieve victory on the field of battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/2b0fb421b1168f4f8a31c20d661c6daa.poster.avif?t=1774177854\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/2b0fb421b1168f4f8a31c20d661c6daa.webm?t=1774177854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/2b0fb421b1168f4f8a31c20d661c6daa.mp4?t=1774177854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modify Tank</h2>During playthrough, you can freely dismantle turrets from your tank and replace it with the turrets from other vehicles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/71d506d3c16a773ed7873aef99269367.poster.avif?t=1774177854\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/71d506d3c16a773ed7873aef99269367.webm?t=1774177854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/71d506d3c16a773ed7873aef99269367.mp4?t=1774177854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recruit Crews</h2>Each student in  the tank club has unique talents. Recruiting them into your crew during battles will grant your vehicle new abilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/794d8a18e0f079a7c9d85b1227dd3836.avif?t=1774177854\" width=600 height=264 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/2e41632d1c5fdfcbc0478de3114f6d82.avif?t=1774177854\" width=600 height=194 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome, comrade Commander!</h2><strong>Multi Turret Academy</strong> is a top-down tank action game with roguelike elements. Select your vehicle from a growing list of historical models, then equip dozens of weapons and upgrades to lead your local tank club to victory!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/9a2e480de691efde49f7d34bba905401.poster.avif?t=1774177854\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/9a2e480de691efde49f7d34bba905401.webm?t=1774177854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/9a2e480de691efde49f7d34bba905401.mp4?t=1774177854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Choice is Yours</h2>A growing selection of WWII tanks awaits, as you decide how to achieve victory on the field of battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/2b0fb421b1168f4f8a31c20d661c6daa.poster.avif?t=1774177854\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/2b0fb421b1168f4f8a31c20d661c6daa.webm?t=1774177854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1869270/extras/2b0fb421b1168f4f8a31c20d661c6daa.mp4?t=1774177854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modify Tank</h2>During playthrough, you can